Alif-lam-meem
Tilka ayatu alkitabi alhakeemi
Hudan warahmatan lilmuhsineena
Allatheena yuqeemoona alssalata wayu/toona alzzakata wahum bial-akhirati hum yooqinoona
Ola-ika ‘ala hudan min rabbihim waola-ika humu almuflihoona
Wamina alnnasi man yashtaree lahwa alhadeethi liyudilla ‘an sabeeli Allahi bighayri ‘ilmin wayattakhithaha huzuwan ola-ika lahum ‘athabun muheenun
Wa-itha tutla ‘alayhi ayatuna walla mustakbiran kaan lam yasma’ha kaanna fee othunayhi waqran fabashshirhu bi’athabin aleemin
Inna allatheena amanoo wa’amiloo alssalihati lahum jannatu alnna’eemi
Khalideena feeha wa’da Allahi haqqan wahuwa al’azeezu alhakeemu
Khalaqa alssamawati bighayri ‘amadin tarawnaha waalqa fee al-ardi rawasiya an tameeda bikum wabaththa feeha min kulli dabbatin waanzalna mina alssama-i maan faanbatna feeha min kulli zawjin kareemin
Hatha khalqu Allahi faaroonee matha khalaqa allatheena min doonihi bali alththalimoona fee dalalin mubeenin
Walaqad atayna luqmana alhikmata ani oshkur lillahi waman yashkur fa-innama yashkuru linafsihi waman kafara fa-inna Allaha ghaniyyun hameedun
Wa-ith qala luqmanu liibnihi wahuwa ya’ithuhu ya bunayya la tushrik biAllahi inna alshshirka lathulmun ‘atheemun
Wawassayna al-insana biwalidayhi hamalat-hu ommuhu wahnan ‘ala wahnin wafisaluhu fee ‘amayni ani oshkur lee waliwalidayka ilayya almaseeru
Wa-in jahadaka ‘ala an tushrika bee ma laysa laka bihi ‘ilmun fala tuti’huma wasahibhuma fee alddunya ma’roofan waittabi’ sabeela man anaba ilayya thumma ilayya marji’ukum faonabbi-okum bima kuntum ta’maloona
Ya bunayya innaha in taku mithqala habbatin min khardalin fatakun fee sakhratin aw fee alssamawati aw fee al-ardi ya/ti biha Allahu inna Allaha lateefun khabeerun
Ya bunayya aqimi alssalata wa/mur bialma’roofi wainha ‘ani almunkari waisbir ‘ala ma asabaka inna thalika min ‘azmi al-omoori
Wala tusa’’ir khaddaka lilnnasi wala tamshi fee al-ardi marahan inna Allaha la yuhibbu kulla mukhtalin fakhoorin
Waiqsid fee mashyika waoghdud min sawtika inna ankara al-aswati lasawtu alhameeri
Alam taraw anna Allaha sakhkhara lakum ma fee alssamawati wama fee al-ardi waasbagha ‘alaykum ni’amahu thahiratan wabatinatan wamina alnnasi man yujadilu fee Allahi bighayri ‘ilmin wala hudan wala kitabin muneerin
Wa-itha qeela lahumu ittabi’oo ma anzala Allahu qaloo bal nattabi’u ma wajadna ‘alayhi abaana awa law kana alshshaytanu yad’oohum ila ‘athabi alssa’eeri
Waman yuslim wajhahu ila Allahi wahuwa muhsinun faqadi istamsaka bial’urwati alwuthqa wa-ila Allahi ‘aqibatu al-omoori
Waman kafara fala yahzunka kufruhu ilayna marji’uhum fanunabbi-ohum bima ‘amiloo inna Allaha ‘aleemun bithati alssudoori
Numatti’uhum qaleelan thumma nadtarruhum ila ‘athabin ghaleethin
Wala-in saaltahum man khalaqa alssamawati waal-arda layaqoolunna Allahu quli alhamdu lillahi bal aktharuhum la ya’lamoona
Lillahi ma fee alssamawati waal-ardi inna Allaha huwa alghaniyyu alhameedu
Walaw annama fee al-ardi min shajaratin aqlamun waalbahru yamudduhu min ba’dihi sab’atu abhurin ma nafidat kalimatu Allahi inna Allaha ‘azeezun hakeemun
Ma khalqukum wala ba’thukum illa kanafsin wahidatin inna Allaha samee’un baseerun
Alam tara anna Allaha yooliju allayla fee alnnahari wayooliju alnnahara fee allayli wasakhkhara alshshamsa waalqamara kullun yajree ila ajalin musamman waanna Allaha bima ta’maloona khabeerun
Thalika bi-anna Allaha huwa alhaqqu waanna ma yad’oona min doonihi albatilu waanna Allaha huwa al’aliyyu alkabeeru
Alam tara anna alfulka tajree fee albahri bini’mati Allahi liyuriyakum min ayatihi inna fee thalika laayatin likulli sabbarin shakoorin
Wa-itha ghashiyahum mawjun kaalththulali da’awoo Allaha mukhliseena lahu alddeena falamma najjahum ila albarri faminhum muqtasidun wama yajhadu bi-ayatina illa kullu khattarin kafoorin
Ya ayyuha alnnasu ittaqoo rabbakum waikhshaw yawman la yajzee walidun ‘an waladihi wala mawloodun huwa jazin ‘an walidihi shay-an inna wa’da Allahi haqqun fala taghurrannakumu alhayatu alddunya wala yaghurrannakum biAllahi algharooru
Inna Allaha ‘indahu ‘ilmu alssa’ati wayunazzilu alghaytha waya’lamu ma fee al-arhami wama tadree nafsun matha taksibu ghadan wama tadree nafsun bi-ayyi ardin tamootu inna Allaha ‘aleemun khabeerun